com.icodici.universa.node

Class ItemResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.icodici.universa.node.ItemResult

  • public class ItemResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The exported state of the item. This object is used to return data for the external (e.g. network) queries. We do not expose local data in direct mode. It is a "structure" of final members, to simplify access and avoid getters.

        The current state of the item in question

      • haveCopy

        public final boolean haveCopy
        true if the node has the copy of approvable item at the moment. Note that the node will discard its copy as soon as the consensus of any sort will be found, or the election will fail (timeout, no quorum, etc)

      • createdAt

        public final @NonNull java.time.ZonedDateTime createdAt
        Time when the item was created on the node. It will be slightly different accross the network

      • expiresAt

        public final @NonNull java.time.ZonedDateTime expiresAt
        Current expiration time. It could be changed if the state is not final. Expired items are discarded by the network.
